title: Converse Takeaway Show at Pitchfork Paris: DIIV "Home"
description:
Before they took to the stage at Pitchfork Paris, DIIV hopped on the Converse bus to play the last in our Pitchfork Takeaway series, and this intimate acoustic set at a Parisian cafe.

Track: "Home"
